Name: autosomal recessive centronuclear myopathy
Definition: A centronuclear myopathy that has_material_basis_in autosomal recessive inheritance.

Name: autosomal dominant centronuclear myopathy
Definition: A centronuclear myopathy that has_material_basis_in autosomal dominant inheritance.

Name: centronuclear myopathy X-linked
Definition: A centronuclear myopathy that has_material_basis_in X-linked inheritance of mutations in MTM1 on Xq28.
